# =============================================================================
# PRODUCTION SECURITY CHECKLIST
# =============================================================================
# 
# Before deploying to production, ensure:
# 
# ✓ All keys are production values (not test/dev)
# ✓ All passwords are strong and unique
# ✓ HTTPS is enforced for all services
# ✓ Database connections are encrypted
# ✓ API rate limiting is configured
# ✓ CORS policies are restrictive
# ✓ Content Security Policy is configured
# ✓ Security headers are enabled
# ✓ Secrets are managed through secure deployment system
# ✓ No secrets are committed to version control
# 
# =============================================================================

# Security Notes:
# - Generate all secrets using cryptographically secure random generators
# - Use different secrets for each environment (dev/staging/prod)
# - Rotate secrets regularly (quarterly recommended)
# - Monitor for secret exposure in logs and error messages
# - Use environment-specific secret management (AWS Secrets Manager, etc.)
# - Enable 2FA for all third-party service accounts
# - Regularly audit and rotate API keys
# - Implement secret scanning in CI/CD pipelines